name: r-dplr
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.7.4" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-dplr
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/dplR_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/dplR/dplR_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: c538be6028c51732e1cc46eba37b54cde5a8f8a4d00de1beadb115bede82d1be

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  skip: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('fortran') }}        # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_fortran') }}  # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-matrix >=1.0_3
    - r-r.utils >=1.32.1
    - r-xml >=2.1_0
    - r-boot
    - r-digest >=0.2.3
    - r-lattice >=0.13_6
    - r-matrixstats >=0.50.2
    - r-plyr >=1.8
    - r-png >=0.1_2
    - r-signal
    - r-stringi >=0.2_3
    - r-stringr >=0.4
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-matrix >=1.0_3
    - r-r.utils >=1.32.1
    - r-xml >=2.1_0
    - r-boot
    - r-digest >=0.2.3
    - r-lattice >=0.13_6
    - r-matrixstats >=0.50.2
    - r-plyr >=1.8
    - r-png >=0.1_2
    - r-signal
    - r-stringi >=0.2_3
    - r-stringr >=0.4

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('dplR')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('dplR')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/AndyBunn/dplR
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: Perform tree-ring analyses such as detrending, chronology building, and cross dating.  Read and write standard file formats used in dendrochronology.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
